children.text: Enough Said spoken word event series event held at Bistro 4 (4040 St. Laurent, Montreal, QC, H2W 1Y8, Canada) on March 13, 1995, hosted by Lee Gotham. Feature performances by Adeena Karasick. Open mic/supporting performances by Supporting by Vince Tinguely, Mitsiko Miller, David Jager, D. Holmes, and Justin McGrail. and more.
